Quickstrike:




Quickstrike froze. He could hear Inferno outside. He kept his voice low. 
"What do ya wanna do?" he asked Megatron. He took a few steps towards the 
face of the door. He guestured to Dark Mouse, trying his best to forget what 
happened a few minutes ago.

He had a bad feeling about this. Remembered Hell Beast's troops busting in 
the door of the command room, where his leg was shot to the Inferno. He 
didn't want that to happen again.
